DataElement.preferredName: Edit Over-ride Case Report Loaded Date
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Date the tumor report is loaded into a central registry computerized processing file for initiation of quality control activities (e.g., visual editing, application of computerized edits, etc.).

DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: The electronic or paper abstract (or source record) is received by the central cancer registry for the respective tumor.
